{"tid":2167201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：瘋傳手機內置COVID19洩行蹤 IT界拆解（李八方）","createTime":"2020-08-21T02:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T03:05:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"426472da41cb2b20c84e8c52ea1062b23970630c","tid":2167201,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:53:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/PQ3FHR4KLJEQ5FA3WQTRFBPMQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FPQ3FHR4KLJEQ5FA3WQTRFBPMQI%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuwbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=4fbadb1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FPQ3FHR4KLJEQ5FA3WQTRFBPMQI%2F&h=9e01aff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/PQ3FHR4KLJEQ5FA3WQTRFBPMQI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：瘋傳手機內置COVID19洩行蹤 IT界拆解（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/llaq9MRAHoHM2SKZQ6Ree6R5b6w=/5912x3940/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MPIYUV3XZZDTPKBT2MQPMBANTE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fllaq9MRAHoHM2SKZQ6Ree6R5b6w%3D%2F5912x3940%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMPIYUV3XZZDTPKBT2MQPMBANTE.jpg&h=649d5502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃浩華<br />\n<br />\n網上瘋傳一張「COVID-19 暴露記錄」圖片，流傳消息話大家手機都被秘密插入一個「COVID 傳感器」，更新手機之後會自動打開功能，令使用者行蹤被追蹤，嚇親唔少人，不過有議員澄清，呢個係Google同Apple合作設計嘅API，唔係可疑程式，亦唔會洩露大家位置，大家唔需要太擔心啦。<br />\n<br />\n資訊科技界議員莫乃光同代表民主派選資訊科技界嘅候選人黃浩華就出post解釋，呢個COVID-19 Exposure Logging 其實唔係App，而係一個應用程式編程介面（API），。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n莫乃光話，港府都研究過整唔整類似嘅App，但最後決定唔用，所以各位唔需要擔心個新功能會令你嘅行蹤送中啦。"},{"pid":"731096ff7fe31496a766804160f80d46b27c8fd4","tid":2167201,"uid":117729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:57:26.000Z","msg":"其實有晒location tracking， 對幾時邊度自己同病者接觸過<br />\n出個alert都好有幫助<br />\n不過將樣野膠到中國人手上又變第2樣野"},{"pid":"9be7ef8508bb808a6024950a9f278a2c84912335","tid":2167201,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"731096ff7fe31496a766804160f80d46b27c8fd4","tid":2167201,"uid":117729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:57:26.000Z","msg":"其實有晒location tracking， 對幾時邊度自己同病者接觸過<br />\n出個alert都好有幫助<br />\n不過將樣野膠到中國人手上又變第2樣野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"用bluetooth唔用location<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7ebab8c2c33eeadbd23f0529610dccb98edbaa","tid":2167201,"uid":117729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9be7ef8508bb808a6024950a9f278a2c84912335","tid":2167201,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"731096ff7fe31496a766804160f80d46b27c8fd4","tid":2167201,"uid":117729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:57:26.000Z","msg":"其實有晒location tracking， 對幾時邊度自己同病者接觸過<br />\n出個alert都好有幫助<br />\n不過將樣野膠到中國人手上又變第2樣野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"用bluetooth唔用location<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"梳，自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}